room_title: Escape room "Hungover" by AdventurEscape in Hartford
room_address: 1 Corporate Dr, Suite 102 Windsor Locks, CT 06096
room_description:
Sunday Morning. 9 AM.

"I am never drinking again!"

What happened last night anyway? Where is my phone... wallet... keys... and where's Dave!?

Saturday Night. 6 PM. Puzzles Bar

A group of friends home for a reunion head down to the local watering hole and get roped into a competitive game of Flip Cup by some regulars. The rest of the night is a blur. 

This action packed drinking game themed* Adventure keeps you on your toes as you try to piece together what happened last night... and find Dave.
